videos.headline: Maryland's Abby Miller helps turn defense into offense
videos.description: Diamond Miller makes a great steal and dishes to Abby Meyers for a quick three on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Maryland's Abby Miller helps turn defense into offense) 2023/01/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maryland's Diamond Miller attacks the rim for a fierce finish
videos.description: Diamond Miller takes it coast-to-coast and finishes strong at the rim over several Rutgers defenders.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Maryland's Diamond Miller attacks the rim for a fierce finish) 2023/01/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maryland's Faith Masonius rolls to the basket and finishes
videos.description: Faith Masonius rolls to the basket and finishes the layup through contact to extend the Terp's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Maryland's Faith Masonius rolls to the basket and finishes) 2023/01/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rutgers' Kassondra Brown finishes in the paint
videos.description: The Scarlet Knights show off their court vision, ending with a Kassondra Brown layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Rutgers' Kassondra Brown finishes in the paint) 2023/01/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rutgers' Kassondra Brown with a tough and-1 finish
videos.description: Kassondra Brown finishes a tough post spin layup through contact for the and-1.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Rutgers' Kassondra Brown with a tough and-1 finish) 2023/01/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rutgers' Kaylene Smikle turns defense into offense
videos.description: Kaylene Smikle takes a steal to the rim for the layup to cut into the Maryland lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Rutgers' Kaylene Smikle turns defense into offense) 2023/01/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rutgers' Abby Streeter hits from way downtown
videos.description: Abby Streeter knocks down a deep three-pointer to close the gap against Maryland.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Rutgers' Abby Streeter hits from way downtown) 2023/01/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maryland's Bri McDaniel with a transition and-1
videos.description: Faith Masonius finds Bri McDaniel down court for a tough and-1 finish in transition for the Terps.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Maryland's Bri McDaniel with a transition and-1) 2023/01/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maryland's Diamond Miller hits the and-1 layup falling down
videos.description: Diamond Miller finishes a tough layup in the lane for an and-1 finish against the Scarlet Knights.
